00:12:22.330 --> 00:12:22.960
Graham...

00:12:25.860 --> 00:12:27.350
¡Espera, padre!

00:12:28.330 --> 00:12:29.960
¡Adónde vas!

00:12:33.560 --> 00:12:35.900
